        "from statsmodels.stats.outliers_influence import variance_inflation_factor\n",
        "\n",
        "X_vif = X_sample.copy()\n",
        "X_vif = X_vif.assign(intercept=1)\n",
        "\n",
        "vif_values = []\n",
        "for i in range(X_vif.shape[1]-1):  # ignora intercepto\n",
        "    vif = variance_inflation_factor(X_vif.values, i)\n",
        "    vif_values.append(vif)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"VIF médio:\", np.mean(vif_values))\n",
        "print(\"VIF máximo:\", np.max(vif_values))"

        "#3) Funções de treino e avaliação (RMSE e R²)\n",
        "def train_one_epoch(model, loader, optimizer, criterion, device):\n",
        "    model.train()\n",
        "    total_loss = 0.0\n",
        "    for xb, yb in loader:\n",
        "        xb, yb = xb.to(device), yb.to(device)\n",
        "\n",
        "        optimizer.zero_grad()\n",
        "        pred = model(xb)\n",
        "        loss = criterion(pred, yb)\n",
        "        loss.backward()\n",
        "        optimizer.step()\n",
        "\n",
        "        total_loss += loss.item() * xb.size(0)\n",
        "\n",
        "    return total_loss / len(loader.dataset)\n",
        "\n",
        "@torch.no_grad()\n",
        "def evaluate(model, loader, device):\n",
        "    model.eval()\n",
        "    y_true_all = []\n",
        "    y_pred_all = []\n",
        "\n",
        "    for xb, yb in loader:\n",
        "        xb = xb.to(device)\n",
        "        pred = model(xb).cpu().numpy().ravel()\n",
        "        y_true = yb.numpy().ravel()\n",
        "\n",
        "        y_true_all.append(y_true)\n",
        "        y_pred_all.append(pred)\n",
        "\n",
        "    y_true_all = np.concatenate(y_true_all)\n",
        "    y_pred_all = np.concatenate(y_pred_all)\n",
        "\n",
        "    mse = mean_squared_error(y_true_all, y_pred_all)\n",
        "    rmse = np.sqrt(mse)\n",
        "    r2 = r2_score(y_true_all, y_pred_all)\n",
        "\n",
        "    return mse, rmse, r2"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "AGX-UQw6CUbR"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []

        "for epoch in range(1, epochs + 1):\n",

        "    mse_te, rmse_te, r2_te = evaluate(model, test_loader, device)\n",
        "\n",

        "\n",
        "    if rmse_te < best_rmse - 1e-4:\n",
        "        best_rmse = rmse_te\n",
        "        best_state = {k: v.cpu().clone() for k, v in model.state_dict().items()}\n",
        "        pat_count = 0\n",
